graph LR
    KubeRay[KubeRay Operator<br/>v1.4.2]

    %% External Dependencies (Required)
    KubeRay -->|resource mgmt| Kubernetes[Kubernetes 1.30+]
    KubeRay -->|controller framework| ControllerRuntime[controller-runtime v0.22.1]

    %% External Dependencies (Optional)
    KubeRay -.->|TLS certs| CertManager[cert-manager v1.x]
    KubeRay -.->|advanced routing| GatewayAPI[Gateway API v1/v1beta1]
    KubeRay -.->|OpenShift ingress| OpenshiftRoute[OpenShift Route API v1]
    KubeRay -.->|metrics| Prometheus[Prometheus]
    KubeRay -.->|GCS HA| Redis[External Redis]
    KubeRay -.->|batch scheduling| BatchSchedulers[Batch Schedulers<br/>Volcano/Kueue]

    %% Cloud Services
    KubeRay -->|model storage| ObjectStorage[Object Storage<br/>S3/GCS]
    KubeRay -->|container images| ContainerRegistry[Container Registry]

    %% Internal RHOAI Dependencies
    OdhDashboard[ODH Dashboard] -.->|displays resources| KubeRay
    ModelRegistry[Model Registry] -.->|distributed training| KubeRay
    DataSciencePipelines[Data Science Pipelines] -.->|executes jobs| KubeRay

    %% Ray Framework (Managed)
    KubeRay -->|deploys| RayFramework[Ray Framework<br/>Distributed Compute]

    %% Subgraph for clarity
    subgraph "Required External"
        Kubernetes
        ControllerRuntime
    end

    subgraph "Optional External"
        CertManager
        GatewayAPI
        OpenshiftRoute
        Prometheus
        Redis
        BatchSchedulers
    end

    subgraph "Cloud Services"
        ObjectStorage
        ContainerRegistry
    end

    subgraph "Internal RHOAI"
        OdhDashboard
        ModelRegistry
        DataSciencePipelines
    end

    subgraph "Managed Workloads"
        RayFramework
    end

